       text-overflow ellipsis, žádný truncate). Desktop drží nowrap pro
       konzistentní 1-line look. */
    .lp-tile__label {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
      white-space: normal;
      text-overflow: clip;
      overflow: visible;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    }
    .lp-tile__sub {
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      white-space: normal;
      text-overflow: clip;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .lp-tile__ribbon path { stroke-width: 44; }
    .lp-tile--reserve .lp-tile__ribbon path { stroke-width: 52; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .lp-tile__sub { display: none; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .lp-tile, .lp-tile__ribbon { transition: none; }
    .lp-tile__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal] path,
    .lp-tile__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal].is-revealed path {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  /* ============ ZIG-ZAG SEKCE (one-pager) ============ */
  .lp-sections {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .lp-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .lp-section:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .lp-section:nth-of-type(even) {
    background: var(--bg-muted);
  }

  /* Section ribbon: thin Bezier curve as background ornament, fills negative
     space opposite the photo + peeká z pod fotky (Z-layer). Sudé sekce dostanou
     scaleX(-1) takže ribbon přejde na druhou stranu. */
  .lp-section__ribbon {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.32;
  }
  .lp-section__ribbon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .lp-section__ribbon path {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-width: 36;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }
  .lp-section__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal] path {
    stroke-dasharray: 1;
    stroke-dashoffset: 1;
    pathLength: 1;
  }
  /* Reveal + idle breathing. Sekce není klikatelná, takže žádný hover. */
  .lp-section__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal].is-revealed path {
    animation:
      ribbon-snake-draw 3.2s var(--ease-snake) forwards,
      ribbon-breathe 7s ease-in-out 3.2s infinite;
  }
  .lp-section:nth-of-type(even) .lp-section__ribbon { transform: scaleX(-1); }

  .lp-section__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    /* Width pattern: content edge se zarovná s tile grid (1480 max,
       gutter-aware na menších viewportech). Žádný vlastní padding-x. */
    width: calc(100% - 2 * var(--gutter));
    max-width: var(--container-wide);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 80px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  /* Sudé sekce: flipnout media doleva, text doprava. */
  .lp-section:nth-of-type(even) .lp-section__media { order: -1; }

  .lp-section__text {
    min-width: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  .lp-section__eyebrow {
    font: 600 var(--text-2xs) / 1 var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lp-section__title {
    font: 600 clamp(1.875rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem) / 1.15 var(--font-sans);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .lp-section__lede {
    font: 400 var(--text-md) / 1.6 var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--fg-soft, var(--fg));
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lp-section__ctas {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }
  /* Sekce CTA, jednotný outline tón napříč zigzagem (plum border + plum text,
     transparentní pozadí, hover swap na solid plum fill).
     Desktop: row layout (arrow vpravo přes flex order vede z následující řádky).
     Mobile (≤ 760): column layout, arrow nad textem, top-left, menší font. */
  .lp-section__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    font: 600 var(--text-sm) / 1 var(--font-sans);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 200ms ease, color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    background: transparent;
  }
  .lp-section__cta:hover,
  .lp-section__cta:focus-visible {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent-on);
    outline: none;
  }
  .lp-section__cta-arrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.05em;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: transform 220ms ease;
  }
  .lp-section__cta-label { line-height: 1; }
  .lp-section__cta:hover .lp-section__cta-arrow,
  .lp-section__cta:focus-visible .lp-section__cta-arrow {
    transform: translate(2px, -2px);
  }
  .lp-section__media { min-width: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .lp-section { padding: var(--space-7) 0; }
    .lp-section__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }
    /* Na mobilu vždy text první, pak média (žádný flip). */
    .lp-section:nth-of-type(even) .lp-section__media { order: 0; }
    .lp-section__ribbon { opacity: 0.32; }
    .lp-section__ribbon path { stroke-width: 32; }

    /* CTA: arrow přesunut na top-left, label pod ním, full-width tlačítko
       takže se nepere s narrow column. Menší font aby se text vlezl bez
       překládání. */
    .lp-section__ctas { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .lp-section__cta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 22px 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      column-gap: 10px;
      row-gap: 4px;
      align-items: start;
      justify-content: start;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .lp-section__cta-arrow {
      grid-row: 1 / 2;
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
      font-size: 18px;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .lp-section__cta-label {
      grid-row: 2 / 3;
      grid-column: 1 / 3;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .lp-section__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal] path,
    .lp-section__ribbon[data-ribbon-reveal].is-revealed path {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  /* ============ SUMMARY CARDS (pod Ubytováním) ============ */
  /* Dvě karty vedle sebe, krátký souhrn dvou produktových košů (Co-living
     vlevo, Privátní apartmány vpravo). Jednoduchá konverzní karta, ne
     per-varianta breakdown. Subtle 2-layer drop shadow, padding, dl s
     uppercase eyebrow labely a tabular-nums na řádku ceny. Mobile stack. */
  .lp-summary {
    width: calc(100% - 2 * var(--gutter));
    max-width: var(--container-wide);
    margin: var(--space-7) auto 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(20px, 2.4vw, 32px);
  }
  .lp-summary__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    padding: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 16px hsl(var(--hue) 41% 13% / 0.06),
      0 12px 32px hsl(var(--hue) 41% 13% / 0.08);
    transition: transform 240ms var(--ease-standard),
                box-shadow 240ms var(--ease-standard);
  }
  .lp-summary__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
